data.description: Welcome home to this almost brand new colonial in the Westfields!   Filled with upgrades from the granite countertops, SS appliances, morning room addition and finished basement.   Fenced in back yard backs to conservation area for added privacy.   The open main floor is perfect for entertaining.  You will feel right at home the moment you walk in the door!  Convenient to 1-70, I-81, shopping, groceries and just a short walk to elementary school!
